#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about calm consequences.\n"
"\n"
"Our actions have consequences. Some consequences happen naturally (‚Äúif you break something, you can‚Äôt use it anymore‚Äù). \n"
"\n"
"Other consequences we set as a family to motivate us to follow the rules (‚Äúif you come home late, you can‚Äôt go out with friends tomorrow‚Äù)."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How will introducing calm consequences help you and your family? Tap play to learn"
