#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings, everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Today's topic is calm consequences.\n"
"\n"
"It is important that when we introduce consequences to our teenagers we involve them, but also important that we are calm when we introduce consequences.\n"
"\n"
"That will assist us to agree on introducing calm consequences to our teenagers, and our teenagers will easily remember them when they are involved and that will make them responsible."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When your teen behaves well you praise them, and when they break an agreed rule you give a calm consequence. \n"
"\n"
"Calm consequences work best when they are fair, agreed on together, and used consistently ‚Äî not in anger."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_male_5.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Agreeing on consequences together works! Tap play to hear @data.characters.media_male_5.name tell his story"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When my teenagers made me angry, I used to shout and punish them right away. I felt so overwhelmed that I even threatened to leave. But nothing changed ‚Äî they still did the same things, even when I shouted.\n"
"\n"
"@global.app_name helped me see that teens listen better when I am calm. Now, when something happens, I take a deep breath and say, ‚ÄòWe will talk about this later when we are both calm.‚Äô\n"
"\n"
"We also agree on consequences together before something goes wrong. This has made a big difference ‚Äî we can resolve problems together, and I feel much less stressed.\n"
"I wish I knew this earlier, but it‚Äôs never too late to start."
msgstr ""

